			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="1. CTY_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;2. Talk to Hope in House of Hope and promise to help&#xD;&#xA;teleport S_LOW_HouseOfHope_HopeIntroduction_Trigger&#xD;&#xA;3. Talk to Eternal Debtor&#xD;&#xA;teleport S_LOW_HouseOfHope_ImpDebtor04" />
