			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="A dialogue with one of the &quot;guards&quot; in House of Hope. &#xD;&#xA;These are Eternal Debtors, each one has a story how did they manage to get into Raphael's hands. &#xD;&#xA;ImpDebtors behave a bit differently: they observe everyone and will watch at players constantly.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;These characters see players as &quot;guests&quot; of House of Hope and they don't know anything about players. " />
